	dprr:hasNoteText "Monetalis. In MRR 2.436, and Index, 549, refer to Crawford, RRC 1.229-230, no. 173, 169-158 B.C. Perhaps a son of C. Cluvius Saxula (14), Pr. 173. See also on Sax(ula?), Crawford, RRC 1.233-234, no. 180, 169-158 B.C., perhaps a younger brother of the above.\n" .
